{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-03112/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-03112"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:31:12"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, tilt"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man puts a dress on a woman."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03112/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-03112","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03112/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-03112"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03112/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03112/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03112/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03112/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03112/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03112/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03112/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03112/canvas/1/df6ef83d-e80e-4d99-8740-0cb4df16ca59","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T13:48:57.004Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Shot from below and with her arms outstretched, Alma resembles a diver in this series of shots, as if she is plunging into the dress that he’s brought her and, therefore, a new life with Reynolds. She takes a metaphorical leap of faith.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03112/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:759.4390507011865,479.41747572815547,825.0269687162893,296.8716289104639"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03112/canvas/1/701b1195-fd96-4f6a-95a5-ccbcef05a907","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T13:49:17.887Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>In the (relatively)&nbsp;least chaste moment of the film, the camera reveals Alma’s underwear. At no other time are any of the characters’ undergarments seen. This moment, then, is a representation of how she and Reynolds have started to bond, to become intimate through this fitting. Indeed, for Reynolds, the act of dressing his future lover is more romantic and more sensual than the opposite.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03112/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:973.4627831715209,857.4110032362462,667.9611650485438,162.24379719525348"}}}]}]}]}